  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: bug needs deeper investigation\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # Can recover account (with ether in Wallet) with seed phrase and password. The only thing recovered is Wallet. Should have same address/public key. Chats with contacts added in the last 1 day might be shown, also public chats.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # Account can be recovered with phrase and password, but Wallet doesn't created (and after manual creating, It's still empty). Account QR address is the same. Acount name is different. Chats and contacts are empty.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Log in with new or existing account\r\n- Profile -> Backup\r\n- Log out\r\n- Log in -> add existing account -> enter Recovery phrase and Password\r\n- Check Wallet and Profile\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.24 (6291) node 7ebe0c3\r\n* Operating System: Android 8.0.0\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nbefore recovery:\r\n![c735d523b82_rs](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42111847/43685426-5021b6a6-98b3-11e8-9f15-766329aef3b8.jpg) ![fc603325a61_rs](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42111847/43685428-503f7574-98b3-11e8-9267-2635d676c793.jpg)\r\n\r\nafter recovery:\r\n![e9300b6af01_rs](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42111847/43685444-73af7630-98b3-11e8-9cb4-61231e40ea7d.jpg) ![63473b072d2_rs](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42111847/43685443-7392fd20-98b3-11e8-9828-ca1818d52e89.jpg) \r\n\r\n\r\n",
